snippet: New England Patriots tight end Rob Gronkowski missed his second consecutive week with a hamstring injury, after he was ruled out for Sunday's game against the Miami Dolphins....
lead_paragraph: New England Patriots tight end Rob Gronkowski missed his second consecutive week with a hamstring injury, after he was ruled out for Sunday's game against the Miami Dolphins.

headline.main: Gronkowski Out Again for Patriots With Hamstring Issue
headline.print_headline: Gronkowski Out Again for Patriots With Hamstring Issue
